# mbsync
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User sascha.wander@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mail/gmail-mutt"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/maildir/gmail/
Inbox ~/maildir/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail-inbox
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel gmail-sent
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :gmail-local:Sent

Channel gmail-drafts
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Near :gmail-local:Drafts

Channel gmail-trash
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Bin"
Near :gmail-local:Trash

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-trash

